text: Mukhamedyanovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Abzanovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 146 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 70 km from Isyangulovo, 23 km from Abzanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Mukhamedyanovo
